data.description: Encompassing 15 acres of lush land, this idyllic estate presents a harmonious blend of a comfortable home, expansive outdoor spaces, a substantial barn, and the potential for bountiful crops. A charming two bedroom one bathroom home welcomes you its cozy ambiance and modern amenities. Featuring the screened in patio! It’s a haven of comfort and tranquility. Despite its secluded feel this property is conveniently located approximately thirty minutes from Dallas for easy access for essentials and city conveniences. A substantial barn stands proudly on the property, offering numerous possibilities. Perfect for livestock, storage, or transforming into a workshop or artist's studio, the options are boundless. Embrace the opportunity to own a slice of rural paradise where the possibilities are as vast as the land itself. Schedule a showing today!
